akka.testkit

CustomEventFilter

case class CustomEventFilter (test: PartialFunction[LogEvent, Boolean], occurrences: Int) extends EventFilter with Product with Serializable

Custom event filter when the others do not fit the bill.

If the partial function is defined and returns true, filter the event.
